	 ,"x4code":null
	,"x4freetext":["The targets were prepared from Merck electronic-grade"
		,"Si containing <2.1*10**-7 atom percent of phosphorus"
		,"and less than one part in 10**9 of other, electrically"
		,"active impurities. The deposits were dried, weighed,"
		,"covered with 99.99% A1 foil, compacted by pressing,"
		,"stacked and mounted in rigid frames for bombardment."
		,"Typical targets contained 10 to 20 mg Si/cm2."]
	}
